00:07:10.183 --> 00:07:14.198
So, in fact, Beethoven has
the same relationship with his audience

00:07:14.222 --> 00:07:15.373
that Bill Gates does.

00:07:15.397 --> 00:07:17.349
He's a software producer,

00:07:17.373 --> 00:07:19.757
and he has to deal with the hardware.

00:07:20.255 --> 00:07:22.419
And what's interesting about this

00:07:22.443 --> 00:07:25.281
